      "content": "it seems like the \"benefits\" are mostly about long term stuff that might not even happen, but the \"downsides\" like jobs and energy bills are real problems people are facing right now. isn't it kind of irresponsible to push this through when we know it's going to hurt so many families in those coal towns?",
